comments: Prince (LAL) engages with Lopez (MIL) during the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Lopez (MIL) briefly grasps Reaves's (LAL) arm in the post but releases as the two players pursue the rebound.
Reaves (LAL) initiates contact to Lillard's (MIL) head while he is airborne and returning to the floor during his jump shot attempt.
Middleton (MIL) swipes down and initiates contact with Prince's (LAL) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Dinwiddie's (LAL) path and does not deliver contact.
Lillard (MIL) brings his hands towards Russell's (LAL) front and marginal contact occurs as he defends during the drive.
Beasley (MIL) is in a vertical position when he makes contact with the ball and incidental contact with Russell's (LAL) arms during the driving shot attempt.
Replay review of the out of bounds called on Russell (LAL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Russell (LAL) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot, which he legally moves after he releases his dribble.

Dinwiddie (LAL) initiates contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) front that affects his SQBR during the drive.  The contact occurs before Antetokounmpo gathers and is in his shooting motion and a non-shooting foul is correctly assessed.
Davis (LAL) places his right hand on Antetokounmpo's (MIL) body while he is airborne, but he does not extend it into him and the contact when he receives the throw-in is marginal.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly wraps his arm around Davis's (LAL) front and grasps his jersey during the rebound, but immediately releases as he deflects the loose ball.
Lillard (MIL) moves alongside Russell's (LAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Beasley (MIL) loses his balance and lands out of bounds while in possession of the ball.
Beasley (MIL) initiates illegal contact with Hachimura's (LAL) head/face during his driving shot attempt.
Dinwiddie (LAL) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Middleton (MIL) establishes screening position in Reaves' (LAL) path and marginal contact occurs as the screen is set.
Reaves (LAL) extends his hand into Lillard's (MIL) body, initiating contact that affects his jump shot attempt.
Lillard (MIL) is in a legal guarding position moving alongside of Dinwiddie's (LAL) path to the basket.
Dinwiddie (LAL) briefly grasps Lillard's (MIL) extended arm, creating the marginal contact between the two players.
The ball goes off of Middleton's (MIL) leg and out of bounds.
Lillard (MIL) steps forward into Reaves' (LAL) space and initiates illegal contact during his jump shot attempt.
Dinwiddie (LAL) places an arm around Antetokounmpo (MIL) as the two players move towards the basket and the contact does not Antetokounmpo's FOM.
Middleton (MIL) reaches in and initiates contact with Russell's (LAL) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) cleanly blocks the shot attempt prior to when the ball reaches its apex.
Lillard (MIL) reaches in and initiates contact with Dinwiddie's (LAL) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Portis (MIL) and Hachimura (LAL) engage during the rebound and Hachimura's momentum carries him forwards and away from the loose ball as Portis releases.
Dinwiddie (LAL) reaches in and initiates contact with Lillard's (MIL) elbow that affects his SQBR.
Hachimura (LAL) initiates illegal contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm, which affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Lillard (MIL) reaches in and initiates contact with Russell (LAL) that affects his SQBR as he attempts to make the pass.
Reaves (LAL) avoids making any contact as he legally contests Lillard's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Lillard (MIL) commits a take foul on Davis (LAL).
